<p>Beautiful.</p>
<p>All <em>we</em> need to do is create a <code>Subscription</code> - via Stripe's API - if they have a plan
in their cart. Before we create the <code>Invoice</code>, add <code>if $cart-&gt;getSubscriptionPlan()</code>:</p>
